        public int compare(java.lang.Object o1,
                   java.lang.Object o2)
        compare. Use Comparable interface through ITypeCheckSortable instead of String class through IRetailSortable. [Warning!][Critical Assumption] 1. A class implementing IRetailSortable also implements ITypeCheckSortable like OM classes. 2. A target object implements Comparable interface.
